{"id": "1295371397597757441", "channel_id": "1295371397597757441", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，本期為大家帶來的是第19期「融災禁區」地圖，以及時靈擺和對應效果與怪物首領。\n\n◆每兩週刷新獎勵與關卡，每個關卡只需要完成普通模式、困難或癲狂模式其中之一。\n◆經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除 血量上限 的約5%，也就是固定值。\n 當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判定為致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n◆同一關卡的各級警示地圖都相同。隨機某波次是落地戰。\n\n▼▼▼\n\n【第1波】特遣紀錄 - 莉莉「故事的魔法」-【商人的慷慨】地圖\n【第2波】無光之境 - 間隙 地圖【混沌6，深海4，血肉2，超維8】\n【第3波】幻夢深潛 - 蘿坦「鯨躍」地圖\n【第4波】特遣紀錄 - 索蕾爾「薔薇禮贊」-【紅色慶典】地圖\n【第5波】落地戰", "timestamp": "2024-10-14T13:03:28.024000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295371401200668682", "filename": "19low.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2703023, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295371397597757441/1295371401200668682/19low.jpg?ex=69cbc620&is=69ca74a0&hm=d894fd5c11b39c6b4779e3f1e10d51301f54078d1aabd51f6615465541276467&"}, {"id": "1295371402328805397", "filename": "19.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3332943, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295371397597757441/1295371402328805397/19.jpg?ex=69cbc621&is=69ca74a1&hm=e4d5ddbf0f4c55a24980f492c5db26f81e19b8ed10de95ba96dad5ee7e60713a&"}, {"id": "1295371403104882749", "filename": "9d830c6416660794.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1434475, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295371397597757441/1295371403104882749/9d830c6416660794.jpg?ex=69cbc621&is=69ca74a1&hm=3fde6067b6b80db92f865933030a2297b6078aa711dee5228285ac9012bd6218&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295371397597757441", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關卡地圖「融災禁區」總覽ⅩⅨ", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
